      "review_text": "Don't Starve Together is great, you get to starve with other people\n\nJokes aside, this game is amazing. My cousin showed me Don't Starve years ago and I fell in love with it.\nOnce Don't Starve Together came out, I was more than excited because I'd get to play with my friends! ...  I play this game mostly alone, but it's still so much fun.\n\n\nKlei Entertainment put a lot of effort into this, it's a detailed, captivating and fun game you can play for hours upon hours. It can get a bit boring after some time, but if you set yourself new goals, or make a new world with different settings (the customization of the World in this game is absolutely AMAZING, you can defintely make it easier or much more difficult, + there's the Workshop for additional, great content) and you get to try out something new everytime, even without changing anything, no world and experience is going to be the same, it's always a new adventure! :D \n\nOverall, this game is preeeeetty good :) Definitely recommend, even if you have no friends! :D If you want to save a buck, get it on sale but I think it is definitely worth it's price.",
      "timestamp_created": 1687249231
